      "text": "Easter Sunday\n\nHe Is Risen!",
      "backgroundColor": "#1e3a8a",
      "textColor": "#ffffff",
      "fontFamily": "Arial",
      "fontSize": 72,
      "backgroundType": "image",
      "backgroundImagePath": "samples/Blog_Three-Crosses_1920x692_V1.png",
      "backgroundImageData": ""
    },
    {
      "text": "The tomb is empty\nDeath is defeated\nJesus is alive!",
      "backgroundColor": "#1e3a8a",
      "textColor": "#ffffff",
      "fontFamily": "Arial",
      "fontSize": 56,
      "backgroundType": "image",
      "backgroundImagePath": "samples/Blog_Three-Crosses_1920x692_V1.png",
      "backgroundImageData": ""
    },
    {
      "text": "Luke 24:6-7\n\nHe is not here; he has risen!\nRemember how he told you, while he was\nstill with you in Galilee: 'The Son of Man\nmust be delivered over to the hands of\nsinners, be crucified and on the third day\nbe raised again.'",
      "backgroundColor": "#1e3a8a",
      "textColor": "#ffffff",
      "fontFamily": "Arial",
      "fontSize": 42,
      "backgroundType": "image",
      "backgroundImagePath": "samples/Blog_Three-Crosses_1920x692_V1.png",
      "backgroundImageData": ""
    },
    {
      "text": "Celebrate with us!",
      "backgroundColor": "#2c5aa0",
      "textColor": "#ffffff",
